The most common reasons for a grey map are:

1. The map container doesn't have explicit height/width
2. Leaflet CSS isn't loaded
3. The map is initialized before the container is ready
4. There's a JavaScript error preventing initialization

This simplified version addresses all these issues by:

· Using explicit inline styles on the map container
· Loading CSS before JS
· Waiting for DOMContentLoaded
· Adding error handling and fallbacks
· Forcing a resize after initialization
